pid":"bac86b2d262c387ff7cbeb0623a643f5b6318f8a","tid":650524,"uid":35193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"佛教善惡係用個心感受 唔係由阿邊個判斷"},{"pid":"14ec510a889be244b6d9e104fe13d090a7ecc95d","tid":650524,"uid":183491,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002649bdfe3ebb1e799bc21c89d1ebd7732c5532","tid":650524,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"《泥犁經》載佛言：「父作不善，子不代受，子作不善，父不代受，善自獲福，惡自受殃。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"信果啲 唔會因爲你係到鳩up幾句 之後唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80462c61bae23d1e1f4140a9fd4a2c56081e0e01","tid":650524,"uid":102320,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"002649bdfe3ebb1e799bc21c89d1ebd7732c5532","tid":650524,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"《泥犁經》載佛言：「父作不善，子不代受，子作不善，父不代受，善自獲福，惡自受殃。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:22:52.000Z","msg":"善惡的慨念是人的慨念, 即所謂世間意。佛家角度只有因果。當你做左一樣人認為是「善」的因, 咁自然會有人類所講「善」的果。同樣地作「惡」因, 自然會有「惡果」。<br />\n<br />\n正如菩薩到人世示現, 佢一樣會有世間「善」事「惡」事發生, 例如貧病老死, 一樣會有刑傷意外, 一樣會有富貴榮華。但係遇到刑傷, 並唔會因此悲傷痛苦, 遇到富貴, 一樣唔會志得意滿。呢個就是所謂有世間事, 無世間意。"},{"pid":"1f86b508afb714c0b73a9c7d7ff6081b581f8feb","tid":650524,"uid":39921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002649bdfe3ebb1e799bc21c89d1ebd7732c5532","tid":650524,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"《泥犁經》載佛言：「父作不善，子不代受，子作不善，父不代受，善自獲福，惡自受殃。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"點解次次佛post你都會爛尾潛水?"},{"pid":"652c5bc2788ead049ae240d2c422fdfa2c433732","tid":650524,"uid":65433,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bac86b2d262c387ff7cbeb0623a643f5b6318f8a","tid":650524,"uid":35193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"佛教善惡係用個心感受 唔係由阿邊個判斷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"都唔講殺人放火打劫果啲啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界好多灰色嘢<br />\n<br />\n咁即係只要我FEEL GOOD就OK?"},{"pid":"ecbc58fa5217055123be83cdcf8a4cfcdee2e59f","tid":650524,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:29:20.000Z","msg":"樓主同佛教有咩深仇大恨?<br />\n<br />\n我可唔可以咁理解Karma: <br />\n<br />\n就好似玩撞磚遊戲<br />\n我闊角度彈粒波出去(善因), 隻game(世界)通常闊角度反彈粒波(善果)<br />\n窄角度彈出去(惡因)就引致窄角度反彈(惡果)<br />\n但闊窄(善惡/樂苦)係我主觀感覺<br />\n喺隻game角度嚟講, 佢只係反彈啲嘢, 無分闊窄<br />\n玩家45度彈粒波入嚟, 佢就45度彈出, 90度入就90度彈出, 當然要睇磚嘅狀態(因緣, 即條件)<br />\nKarma就係個反彈機制同現象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/112538_51307265aeeb82d642ea0cb7b097653e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F112538_51307265aeeb82d642ea0cb7b097653e.jpg&h=d3c73744&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b0cb9556e7f0fba0a11c84a956d841ea31edd55","tid":650524,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"652c5bc2788ead049ae240d2c422fdfa2c433732","tid":650524,"uid":65433,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bac86b2d262c387ff7cbeb0623a643f5b6318f8a","tid":650524,"uid":35193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"佛教善惡係用個心感受 唔係由阿邊個判斷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"都唔講殺人放火打劫果啲啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界好多灰色嘢<br />\n<br />\n咁即係只要我FEEL GOOD就OK?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"應該唔只係你個人點諗，而係個世界點諗<br />\n<br />\n世界既諗法，有一部份係物理法則既因果<br />\n有一部份，係世界中其他生物既諗法<br />\n<br />\n你殺咗人，就會有人憎恨你；響戰爭殺人，有人會歌頌你<br />\n殺人本身係冇善惡之分，果報亦冇善惡之分<br />\n但胡亂殺生必然導致憎恨，甚至報復<br />\n對一般人黎講，憎恨／報復唔係佢想要既野，係壞事，係惡報"}]}